the values assigned to the Species s1, s2, .... ProductForm[expr, {s1, s2, \
..., {s3, s4, ...}, ...}] splits each Ket[<|...|>] in expr into the form \
Ket[b1]\\[CircleTimes]Ket[b2]\\[CircleTimes]...\\[CircleTimes]Ket[b3, b4, \
